Vanessa Marshall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanessa_Marshall 0 Vanessa Marshall (born October 19, 1969) is an American actress, singer and model. She is most active in voice-over roles for animated series, films and video games. She is the only child of actress Joan Van Ark and reporter John Marshall. She began voice-over work after being discovered at a one-woman show. Vanessa_Marshall ( born October_19_,_1969 ) is an_American_actress , singer_and_model .
